      "text": "[REDACTED] informed him that [REDACTED] had not yet been contacted, but that the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation was \"setting a trap for him\". [REDACTED] further b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "advises that on Friday, August 8, 1947, he appeared before Lawyer [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "at the County-City Building, Seattle and made a deposition of the facts relating",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "to the incidents in Tacoma from Thursday afternoon, July 31, last until Sunday",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "morning, August 3, last.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "A copy of this deposition is now in possession of the writer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "and is being forwarded herewith to the Bureau. It should be noted that this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "deposition is in no way as complete as the statement taken by the writer above",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "and any setting out of this deposition in this communication would be superfluous.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Copies of this communication are being sent to the Butte,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Portland, San Francisco and Chicago Offices for their information only. Unless",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "advised by the Bureau to the contrary, instant investigation is considered closed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "by this office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "For the information of the Bureau, Captain [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
