      "text": "Forces Headquarters at Washington, D. C., during which call the Public Relations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Officer was requested to obtain a signed statement from [REDACTED] which",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
